{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-parent-file-name-js","path":"/v1-30-14-k3s1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"parent":{"name":"v1.30.14+k3s1"},"html":"<!-- v1.30.14+k3s1 -->\n<p>This release updates Kubernetes to v1.30.14, and fixes a number of issues.</p>\n<p>For more details on what's new, see the <a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/CHANGELOG/CHANGELOG-1.30.md#changelog-since-v13013\">Kubernetes release notes</a>.</p>\n<h2>Changes since v1.30.13+k3s1:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Backports for 2025-06 <a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/k3s/pull/12499\">(#12499)</a></li>\n<li>Bump helm-controller <a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/k3s/pull/12521\">(#12521)</a></li>\n<li>Update network components <a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/k3s/pull/12516\">(#12516)</a></li>\n<li>Update to v1.30.14-k3s1 and Go 1.23.10 <a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/k3s/pull/12532\">(#12532)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Embedded Component Versions</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Component</th>\n<th>Version</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Kubernetes</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/CHANGELOG/CHANGELOG-1.30.md#v13014\">v1.30.14</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Kine</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/kine/releases/tag/v0.13.15\">v0.13.15</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SQLite</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://sqlite.org/releaselog/3_49_1.html\">3.49.1</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Etcd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/etcd/releases/tag/v3.5.21-k3s1\">v3.5.21-k3s1</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Containerd</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/containerd/releases/tag/v1.7.27-k3s1\">v1.7.27-k3s1</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Runc</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/opencontainers/runc/releases/tag/v1.2.6\">v1.2.6</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Flannel</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/flannel-io/flannel/releases/tag/v0.27.0\">v0.27.0</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Metrics-server</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/metrics-server/releases/tag/v0.7.2\">v0.7.2</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Traefik</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/traefik/traefik/releases/tag/v2.11.24\">v2.11.24</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CoreDNS</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/coredns/coredns/releases/tag/v1.12.1\">v1.12.1</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Helm-controller</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/helm-controller/releases/tag/v0.16.11\">v0.16.11</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Local-path-provisioner</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://github.com/rancher/local-path-provisioner/releases/tag/v0.0.31\">v0.0.31</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Helpful Links</h2>\n<p>As always, we welcome and appreciate feedback from our community of users. Please feel free to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rancher/k3s/issues/new/choose\">Open issues here</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://slack.rancher.io/\">Join our Slack channel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://rancher.com/docs/k3s/latest/en/\">Check out our documentation</a> for guidance on how to get started or to dive deep into K3s.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rancher/k3s/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">Read how you can contribute here</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"f413a64a-1e5f-5ff8-9766-4cdb6d153d3b","parent__name":"v1.30.14+k3s1","__params":{"parent__name":"v1-30-14-k3s1"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"],"slicesMap":{}}